ROLEX 1933

00:00:00

Description

Rolex, a luxury Swiss watch manufacturer, has a rich history dating back to the early 20th century.
The 1920s was a pivotal decade for Rolex, as it marked the brand's increasing prominence in the watch industry.
During this time, Rolex made significant advancements in watchmaking, helping to establish its reputation for precision and innovation.
